Package: libharfbuzz0
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Section: libs
Multi-Arch: same
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenType text shaping engine
 HarfBuzz is the meat of the modern GNU/Linux text rendering stack. With
 OpenType emerging as the universal font format supporting complex text
 rendering, HarfBuzz, as an OpenType Layout engine, is where all the magic
 happens.
